resolution.description: All attempts at reproducing this issue failed, or not enough information was available to reproduce the issue. Reading the code produces no clues as to why this behavior would occur. If more information appears later, please reopen the issue.

fields.description:
h3. Steps to Reproduce
Start Titanium. Dashboard is empty except for a banner.

h3. Actual Result
Dashboard is empty except for a banner.

h3. Expected Result
A fully functional dashboard.

comments.body:
Hello,

two things here:

- From your log, you are using JDK 1.7. From the docs, you need to use JDK 1.6 32 bits. More info here: http://docs.appcelerator.com/titanium/latest/#!/guide/Prerequisites 

- Are you behind a proxy? You need to configure your proxy inside Ti Studio. http://docs.appcelerator.com/titanium/3.0/#!/guide/Using_Studio_From_Behind_a_Proxy

Best
Please use this ticket, and don't open new ones about this same issue.
I have updated the log file after changing the java version to 1.6 32 bit. The dashboard still does not load. Also, I am not using a proxy. Thank you.
